cat <<'EOF'
Dependencies:
- curl: For downloading Zig binaries
- tar: For extracting archives (with xz support)
- xz: For decompressing .tar.xz archives

On Debian/Ubuntu: apt install curl tar xz-utils
On Fedora: dnf install curl tar xz
On macOS: brew install xz (curl and tar are pre-installed)
EOF
